						<lb/>
						<persName facs="#zone_sb4_n3t_wqb">İsmāʿīl</persName> Beyg(?)
						<lb/> ve gayrihim mine'l-hāzırīn </p>
				</div2>
				<div2 type="note">
					<p>
						<lb/> Be-her ... kırk pāre virmek şütra(?) </p>
